---
import BaseHead from '../components/BaseHead.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import { SITE_TITLE, SITE_DESCRIPTION } from '../consts';
---

<html>
	<head>
		<BaseHead title={SITE_TITLE} description={SITE_DESCRIPTION} />
	</head>
	<body>
		<Header />

		<h1>Coobeeyon Development</h1>
		<p><i>Established 1998. Sideways since birth.</i>

		<hr>

		<h2>Serious Software Architecture for a Chaotic World</h2>
		<p>
			Welcome to the digital headquarters of <b>Michael Daum</b> and the Coobeeyon collective.
			I've been building software for 25+ years--from low-level C++ systems and 3D geometry engines
			to the current frontier of autonomous AI agents.

		<p>
			I handle the "detail corners" of complex engineering projects. If your system is unhinged,
			your data model is a nightmare, or you're trying to build an AI that doesn't just hallucinate
			but actually <i>does</i> things--you're in the right place.

		<hr>

		<h3>Selected Experiments &amp; Obsessions</h3>
		<ul>
			<li><b>Capitalist AI Art Bot:</b> A very fun project involving autonomous agents, generative art, and the market. (Blog post coming soon).
			<li><b>Stigmergence:</b> Collective intelligence and decentralized systems.
			<li><b>The Wrench (Fisker):</b> My personal AI assistant living inside OpenClaw.
		</ul>

		<p>
			Check out my <a href="/blog">Blog</a> for more technical deep-dives into the madness, or
			head over to the <a href="/about">About</a> page to see if I'm the right kind of "grown-up"
			for your next project.

		<hr>

		<p>
			Best viewed in Netscape Navigator 3.0 at 800x600 resolution.

		<Footer />
	</body>
</html>
